txt.en: Fighting in the Ettenmoors, and completing the requests here, will earn you greater rewards. There are a series of important objectives, found throughout the Ettenmoors, that must be undertaken.
Complete a support quest in the Ettenmoors ([placeholder]/21)
Battling in the Ettenmoors, greatly rewards those who are consistent participants. Complete this quest to earn your share of the rewards.
Advancement toward the weekly war effort ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
'Are you willing to undertake the same tasks again, my friend?\n\n'If so, the rewards will be here for your effort.'
